# Secure Rate Limit API

ASP.NET Core Web API project implementing:

- JWT Authentication
- Refresh Tokens
- Role Based Authorization
- Redis Rate Limiting
- API Logging Middleware
- SQL Server with EF Core

## Tech Stack

ASP.NET Core  
Redis  
SQL Server  
JWT Authentication  
Entity Framework Core  

## Features

Authentication system using JWT

Refresh token support

Role based authorization

Redis rate limiting (100 requests/min)

API request logging middleware

## Setup

1 Clone repo

2 Setup SQL Server connection in appsettings.json

3 Run migrations

dotnet ef migrations add InitialCreate
dotnet ef database update

4 Run project

dotnet run

## Endpoints

POST /api/auth/register

POST /api/auth/login

GET /api/test/user (Requires Auth)

GET /api/test/admin (Admin only)

## Rate Limiting

100 requests per minute per IP using Redis
